OL,3,CChildren's Hospice's mission raise #13
OL,4,Cmillion after expansion plans approved
OL,6,FPlans to expand a children's hospice
OL,7,Fin Liverpool have been approved by the
OL,8,Fcity council.
OL,10,FClaire House Hospice provides care for
OL,11,Fseriously ill children across
OL,12,FMerseyside and Cheshire, and now plans
OL,13,Fto offer round the clock care at their
OL,14,Fsecond site in West Derby.
OL,16,FThe plans would transform the
OL,17,Fcharity's West Derby site into a full
OL,18,Fchildren's hospice, bringing vital
OL,19,Fcare closer to home for hundreds of
OL,20,Fseriously ill children across
OL,21,FMerseyside.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
