PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1783064870
OL,3,CChildren's Hospice's mission raise #13
OL,4,Cmillion after expansion plans approved
OL,6,FFor many families, distance has long
OL,7,Fbeen one of the biggest barriers to
OL,8,Faccessing hospice care when they need
OL,9,Fit most. Long, exhausting journeys to
OL,10,Fthe charity's Wirral hospice have
OL,11,Foften meant families spending precious
OL,12,Ftime travelling, rather than being
OL,13,Ftogether.
OL,15,FMum Kate Jones, from Warrington, whose
OL,16,Fson Josh was supported by Claire House
OL,17,Ffor most of his life said:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1783064870
OL,3,CChildren's Hospice's mission raise #13
OL,4,Cmillion after expansion plans approved
OL,6,F"We always wanted our son Josh to pass
OL,7,Fat Claire House, but he was too ill to
OL,8,Fbe transferred to the Wirral site. It
OL,9,Fwas just too far.
OL,11,F"If the West Derby site was up and
OL,12,Frunning, we absolutely would have
OL,13,Fpreferred him to be transferred so he
OL,14,Fcould pass there instead of in the
OL,15,Fhospital. We wouldn't have chosen a
OL,16,Fhospital for him."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
