CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1783064870
OL,3,CChildren's Hospice's mission raise #13
OL,4,Cmillion after expansion plans approved
OL,6,FWith 60% of Claire House referrals now
OL,7,Fcoming from Liverpool and the
OL,8,Fsurrounding area, today's announcement
OL,9,Fmarks a major milestone in ensuring
OL,10,Fchildren get the expert care they
OL,11,Fneed, right where they need it.
OL,13,FThere are many children and families
OL,14,Fwho need Claire House that the charity
OL,15,Fis not currently reaching, 80% of
OL,16,Fwhich are in Liverpool and the
OL,17,Fsurrounding areas.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
