PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1783064870
OL,3,CChildren's Hospice's mission raise #13
OL,4,Cmillion after expansion plans approved
OL,6,FDavid Pastor, CEO of Claire House,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We couldn't do this without the
OL,8,Fgenerosity of people in the region, so
OL,9,Fthank you to the people who support us
OL,10,Fand now we've got planning permission
OL,11,Fwe can really get on with the
OL,12,Ffundraising side of things to get hold
OL,13,Fof hopefully the other #13 million
OL,14,Fthat we need"
OL,16,F"We are absolutely delighted that
OL,17,Fplanning permission has now been
OL,18,Fapproved.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
