PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1783064870
OL,3,CChildren's Hospice's mission raise #13
OL,4,Cmillion after expansion plans approved
OL,6,F"Every day at Claire House, I'm
OL,7,Freminded that when a baby, child or
OL,8,Fyoung adult is seriously ill, there is
OL,9,Fonly one chance to get their care
OL,10,Fright. We cannot change a diagnosis or
OL,11,Fstop children dying but we can make
OL,12,Fsure families feel supported,
OL,13,Funderstood, and surrounded by
OL,14,Fcompassion when it matters most."
OL,16,FJill Jones's from Orrell Park,
OL,17,FLiverpool is mum to four-year-old
OL,18,FJoshy Farrell.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1783064870
OL,3,CChildren's Hospice's mission raise #13
OL,4,Cmillion after expansion plans approved
OL,6,FShe said: "Any temperature means a
OL,7,F48hour hospital stay for Joshy ` so
OL,8,Fhaving Claire House Liverpool just 15
OL,9,Fminutes from home, and right next to
OL,10,FAlder Hey, gives us the reassurance we
OL,11,Fdesperately need."
OL,13,F"So many children need this place, it
OL,14,Fbenefits everyone. It's reassuring for
OL,15,Ffamilies to know if their child had
OL,16,Fcomplex needs, they'd be in safe
OL,17,Fhands. It's a community."
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
