OL,3,CChildren's Hospice's mission raise #13
OL,4,Cmillion after expansion plans approved
OL,6,FThe approved plans would see the
OL,7,Ftransformation of a former monastery
OL,8,Finto a purpose-built hospice
OL,9,Fenvironment.
OL,11,FThe newly approved development would
OL,12,Finclude:
OL,14,FClaire House will now move into the
OL,15,Fnext phase, raising the funds and
OL,16,Fsupport needed to bring this essential
OL,17,Ffacility into a full hospice for
OL,18,FLiverpool's children and families.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
